  "description": "This individual presents as an undead human whose dried features and slack posture mark prolonged exposure to death’s desiccating tenure. Gray eyes sit deep in a light, fissured face, and brown hair lies in sparse, brittle lengths that no longer hold a living sheen. The mouth and jaw set in an uneven line, suggesting old fractures that healed without care and remain permanently misaligned. The overall build is wiry and undernourished, with rigid hands and forearms hardened into a laborer’s lasting shape.",
